title: fmt.Printf %#v changed
body:
This changeset:

   changeset:   13342:23c7da226e28
   user:        Rob Pike <r@golang.org>
   date:        Tue May 29 15:08:08 2012 -0700
   summary:     fmt: speed up 10-20%

Made this:

   fmt.Printf("%#v", "foo")

Output `foo` instead of "foo". The log makes me think it's an oversight.
